    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="I&#39;d like to have an in-depth discussion about a request. Can I use the pixiv Message feature to communicate?" class="article-title">
          I&#39;d like to have an in-depth discussion about a request. Can I use the pixiv Message feature to communicate?
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p><span>Communication outside of the Requests feature is prohibited.<br>Please refrain from asking for additions or changes to the content of a request or to specify a deadline in pixiv Messages, comments, etc.<br><br>Please understand that if you communicate outside of the Requests feature before or after sending a request, it is possible that it may interfere with the creator's creative process.<br><br>Similarly, communication outside of the feature may cause issues and misunderstandings such as modifications to the deadline and/or content, as well as requests for changes or retakes.</span></p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

